  "disabilityGapEduCoBody": "Under art. 324a CO, the employer must pay the salary for a limited period in case of illness. This duration depends on years of service and the applicable cantonal scale (Bernese, Zurich or Basel). After this period, only the IJM (if any) takes over.",
