  "challengeBudget02Title": "Calculate your real monthly savings rate",
  "challengeBudget02Desc": "Your savings rate is what's left after all expenses. Check whether it exceeds 10% of your net income.",
  "challengeBudget03Title": "Compare your insurance costs with an alternative offer",
  "challengeBudget03Desc": "Insurance premiums can vary by 30% between providers. Check whether you could save by switching.",
  "challengeBudget04Title": "Analyse your fixed vs variable expenses",
  "challengeBudget04Desc": "Separate fixed costs (rent, insurance) from variable ones (outings, leisure). This is the foundation for optimising your budget.",
  "challengeBudget05Title": "Check your debt ratio",
  "challengeBudget05Desc": "Your debt ratio should not exceed 33% of gross income. Calculate it to see where you stand.",
  "challengeBudget06Title": "Simulate the real cost of your lease",
  "challengeBudget06Desc": "A lease is more than the monthly payment: insurance, maintenance, residual value. Calculate the total cost.",
  "challengeBudget07Title": "Evaluate your emergency fund in months",
  "challengeBudget07Desc": "How many months could you last without income? The ideal is 3 to 6 months of expenses.",
  "challengeBudget08Title": "Check whether you could reduce your consumer credit",
  "challengeBudget08Desc": "Consumer credit at 8-12% is very expensive. See if you can accelerate repayment or consolidate it.",

  "challengeEpargne01Title": "Set aside CHF\u00a050 this week",
  "challengeEpargne01Desc": "Even a small amount counts: CHF\u00a050 per week is CHF\u00a02,600 per year. The hardest part is starting.",
  "challengeEpargne02Title": "Check your 3a balance vs the ceiling",
  "challengeEpargne02Desc": "The 3a ceiling for employees is CHF\u00a07,258 per year. Check how much you have already contributed this year.",
  "challengeEpargne03Title": "Simulate an LPP buyback of CHF\u00a05,000",
  "challengeEpargne03Desc": "An LPP buyback is tax-deductible. Simulate the impact of a CHF\u00a05,000 buyback on your pension and taxes.",
  "challengeEpargne04Title": "Check whether you can still contribute to 3a this year",
  "challengeEpargne04Desc": "3a contributions are annual: if you haven't reached the maximum yet, there may still be time.",
  "challengeEpargne05Title": "Compare the returns on your 3a accounts",
  "challengeEpargne05Desc": "Not all 3a accounts are equal. Compare your account returns with the simulator.",
  "challengeEpargne06Title": "Calculate the real return on your 3a after inflation",
  "challengeEpargne06Desc": "A 1% return with 1.5% inflation is a negative real return. Check your situation.",
  "challengeEpargne07Title": "Simulate a staggered withdrawal from your 3a accounts",
  "challengeEpargne07Desc": "Withdrawing your 3a over several years can reduce tax. Simulate the staggered withdrawal strategy.",
  "challengeEpargne08Title": "Check whether you can contribute retroactively to 3a",
  "challengeEpargne08Desc": "Since 2025, you can make up years without contributions. Check whether you are eligible for retroactive 3a.",
  "challengeEpargne09Title": "Check your vested benefits if you changed employer",
  "challengeEpargne09Desc": "When changing jobs, your LPP capital is transferred to a vested benefits account. Check that nothing was forgotten.",

  "challengePrevoyance01Title": "Request your AVS account extract",
  "challengePrevoyance01Desc": "Your AVS extract shows your contribution years and estimated pension. Request it for free at lavs.ch.",
  "challengePrevoyance02Title": "Check your disability coverage",
  "challengePrevoyance02Desc": "In case of disability, does your AI + LPP pension cover your expenses? Check the potential gap.",
  "challengePrevoyance03Title": "Compare pension vs lump sum for your LPP",
  "challengePrevoyance03Desc": "Lifetime pension or lump sum? Each option has its tax and flexibility advantages. Compare the scenarios.",
  "challengePrevoyance04Title": "Check your retirement projection",
  "challengePrevoyance04Desc": "Imagine your retirement: AVS + LPP + 3a — how much will you really have? Check whether you're on the right track. Every year counts.",
  "challengePrevoyance05Title": "Optimise your decumulation sequence",
  "challengePrevoyance05Desc": "The order in which you withdraw from your pillars has a major tax impact. Simulate different sequences.",
  "challengePrevoyance06Title": "Check your AVS gaps",
  "challengePrevoyance06Desc": "Each year without AVS contributions reduces your pension — the impact can be significant over the long term. Check for any gaps to fill.",
  "challengePrevoyance07Title": "Plan your succession",
  "challengePrevoyance07Desc": "Who inherits what under Swiss law? Check the reserved shares and whether a will is needed.",
  "challengePrevoyance08Title": "Check your unemployment coverage",
  "challengePrevoyance08Desc": "Losing your job is stressful. Knowing how much you would receive and for how long can reassure you. Simulate your situation.",
  "challengePrevoyance09Title": "Check your disability coverage as self-employed",
  "challengePrevoyance09Desc": "As self-employed, your AI coverage may be insufficient. Check whether a supplementary daily allowance insurance would be useful.",

  "challengeFiscalite01Title": "Estimate your 3a tax saving",
  "challengeFiscalite01Desc": "Every franc contributed to 3a is deductible. Calculate how much you save in taxes this year.",
  "challengeFiscalite02Title": "Check whether an LPP buyback would be deductible this year",
  "challengeFiscalite02Desc": "LPP buybacks are deductible from taxable income. Check your buyback potential and the tax saving.",
  "challengeFiscalite03Title": "Simulate the tax on a capital withdrawal",
  "challengeFiscalite03Desc": "Capital withdrawals (LPP/3a) are taxed separately at a reduced rate. Simulate the tax for different amounts.",
  "challengeFiscalite04Title": "Compare salary vs dividend if you are self-employed",
  "challengeFiscalite04Desc": "The salary/dividend mix for your situation depends on your income and canton. Simulate both scenarios.",
  "challengeFiscalite05Title": "Check the imputed rental value of your property",
  "challengeFiscalite05Desc": "If you own property, the imputed rental value is added to your taxable income. Check whether it is correct.",
  "challengeFiscalite06Title": "Calculate your total tax burden",
  "challengeFiscalite06Desc": "Federal + cantonal + communal tax: calculate your total tax burden as a percentage of your income.",
  "challengeFiscalite07Title": "Check your FATCA compliance",
  "challengeFiscalite07Desc": "As a US citizen, your Swiss accounts are subject to FATCA. Check that your situation is in order.",
  "challengeFiscalite08Title": "Check your withholding tax",
  "challengeFiscalite08Desc": "As a cross-border commuter, you are taxed at source. Check that the rate applied matches your situation.",

  "challengePatrimoine01Title": "Calculate your mortgage borrowing capacity",
  "challengePatrimoine01Desc": "Using the 1/3 rule, check how much you could borrow for a property purchase.",
  "challengePatrimoine02Title": "Simulate SARON vs fixed rate for your mortgage",
  "challengePatrimoine02Desc": "SARON (variable) or fixed rate? Simulate both scenarios over 10 years to see the difference.",
  "challengePatrimoine03Title": "Compare renting vs owning",
  "challengePatrimoine03Desc": "Buying is not always better than renting. Compare both options over 20 years with the simulator.",
  "challengePatrimoine04Title": "Simulate an EPL (early LPP withdrawal for housing)",
  "challengePatrimoine04Desc": "You can use your 2nd pillar to finance your home. Simulate the impact on your retirement.",
  "challengePatrimoine05Title": "Review your complete wealth balance sheet",
  "challengePatrimoine05Desc": "Assets, liabilities, net worth: take stock of your overall financial situation. An important moment for perspective.",
  "challengePatrimoine06Title": "Check your annual savings allocation",
  "challengePatrimoine06Desc": "Between 3a, LPP buyback and mortgage amortisation, how should you distribute your savings this year? Each choice has a different tax impact.",
  "challengePatrimoine07Title": "Simulate the impact of mortgage amortisation",
  "challengePatrimoine07Desc": "Amortise directly or indirectly via 3a? Simulate both options and their tax impact.",
  "challengePatrimoine08Title": "Simulate the effect of compound interest over 20 years",
  "challengePatrimoine08Desc": "Even a small return creates a snowball effect. Simulate the growth of your savings over 20 years.",

  "challengeEducation01Title": "Read the article on the 13th AVS pension",
  "challengeEducation01Desc": "Since 2026, the 13th AVS pension increases your annual pension. Discover what this means concretely for you.",
  "challengeEducation02Title": "Understand the difference between minimum and supra-mandatory conversion rates",
  "challengeEducation02Desc": "The LPP conversion rate of 6.8% only applies to the minimum. Your fund may have a different rate for the supra-mandatory portion.",
  "challengeEducation03Title": "Discover how the 1st pillar works",
  "challengeEducation03Desc": "The AVS is a pay-as-you-go system: working people fund retirees. Understand the basics of your future pension.",
  "challengeEducation04Title": "Understand the 3-pillar system",
  "challengeEducation04Desc": "AVS + LPP + 3a: each pillar has its role. Understand how they complement each other for your retirement.",
  "challengeEducation05Title": "Explore the concept of replacement rate",
  "challengeEducation05Desc": "The replacement rate measures the ratio between your pension and your last salary. The common target is 60-80%.",
  "challengeEducation06Title": "Understand LPP contributions by age bracket",
  "challengeEducation06Desc": "LPP contributions increase with age: 7%, 10%, 15%, 18%. Check which bracket you are in.",
  "challengeEducation07Title": "Discover the financial consequences of cohabitation",
  "challengeEducation07Desc": "In cohabitation, you do not have the same inheritance rights as a married person. Check the necessary protections.",
  "challengeEducation08Title": "Understand the impact of the gender gap on retirement",
  "challengeEducation08Desc": "Women receive on average 37% less pension. Understand the causes and possible solutions.",

  "challengeArchetypeEu01Title": "Check your EU contribution years for AVS",
  "challengeArchetypeEu01Desc": "Thanks to bilateral agreements, your years contributed in the EU count towards your Swiss AVS pension. Request an E205 certificate to verify the totalisation.",
  "challengeArchetypeNonEu01Title": "Check whether a social security convention covers your country",
  "challengeArchetypeNonEu01Desc": "Without a bilateral agreement, your foreign contributions do not count for AVS. Check whether your home country has an agreement with Switzerland.",
  "challengeArchetypeReturning01Title": "Check your LPP buyback potential after returning to Switzerland",
  "challengeArchetypeReturning01Desc":"Back in Switzerland after a stay abroad? You may have significant LPP buyback potential, tax-deductible. Simulate the amount.",
  "nudgeSalaryBody": "Have you thought about your 3a transfer this month? Every month counts for your retirement savings.",
  "nudgeTaxDeadlineTitle": "Tax filing deadline",
  "nudgeTaxDeadlineBody": "Check the tax filing deadline in your canton. Have you reviewed your 3a and LPP deductions?",
  "nudge3aDeadlineTitle": "Final stretch for your 3a",
  "nudge3aDeadlineBody": "{days} day(s) left to contribute up to {limit} CHF and reduce your {year} taxes.",
  "nudgeBirthdayBody": "A milestone that could shape your retirement planning. Have you simulated the impact of this year?",
  "nudgeProfileTitle": "Your profile deserves to be enriched",
  "nudgeProfileBody": "The more complete your profile, the more relevant insights MINT can offer. Just a few details needed.",
  "nudgeInactiveTitle": "It has been a while!",
  "nudgeInactiveBody": "Your financial situation evolves every week. Take 2 minutes to check your dashboard.",
  "nudgeGoalProgressTitle": "Your goal is progressing!",
  "nudgeGoalProgressBody": "You have reached {progress}% of your goal. Keep going!",
  "nudgeAnniversaryBody": "You have been using MINT for a year. It is the perfect time to update your profile and measure your progress.",
  "nudgeLppBuybackTitle": "LPP buyback window",
